latestPosts.caption:
Elevitta Mrs. India – Batch 1 Auditions
Every story mattered. Every voice was heard.
With grace and empathy, our esteemed jury — Alesia Raut, Serena Khat, Sargam Koushal, and Avani Kakekochhi — listened to each woman as she poured her heart out.

A day filled with dreams, laughter, learning, and unforgettable connections. 
This wasn’t just an audition — it was the start of a transformation. 

#ElevittaMrsIndia #Batch1 #WomensVoicesMatter #PageantWithPurpose #SerenaKhat #SargamKoushal #AlesiaRaut #AvaniKakekochhi #dreambelieveachieve 

Are you the next Mrs World?

latestPosts.caption:
It’s official. It’s real. It’s HERE.
We are beyond thrilled to announce the launch of Elevitta Mrs India World @elevittamrsindiaworld – a celebration of strength, beauty, purpose, and power.

A heartfelt thank you to @mrsworldpageant, the Mrs. World Organization, and the incredible team at Mrs. World Inc. for placing their trust in us. We are honoured to hold the official national directorship license for India. 

This moment is more than a milestone – it’s a legacy in the making.

Here’s to every woman who’s ever dreamed big. The stage is yours now.

Let the crown journey begin.

With love,
Sargam Koushal & Serena Khat
@sargam3 @serenakhat 
National Directors,
